        <p class="text-[#dfe2eb] mt-2">Using his own words, Jos&eacute; Luis is <cite class="text-[#c9c8ad] italic">"just a lucky person in love with my family and my work. I've always been a Visual Designer. Everywhere I look, I see design and taste. I'm an essence searcher who admires simplicity. That's why Design is essential for me, since it 's the ultimate expression and shape of everything."</cite></p>
