        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-[#dfe2eb]">Art Champoux</h4>
        <span class="uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-[#D7DF21]">UFO Investigator</span>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
