        <p class="text-[#dfe2eb] mt-4"><strong class="text-[#dfe2eb]">CISU</strong> stands for <strong class="text-[#dfe2eb]">Centro Italiano Studi Ufologici</strong>. The Italian Center for UFO Studies was founded in 1985, as a merging from three different experiences:</p>
